      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IN THE SNOW (1) struggling for winning form, but gets every chance from the inside. Last time finished 6th in a Maiden on February 20 over 300m at Healesville behind Extreme Dash beaten 4.5 lengths (17.45). Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. ACCIDENTAL (2) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 9 lengths away in sixth (23.16). Was in the money the start prior. The form out of last race has been strong. Cannot be left out. PSEUDO (7) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (23.48) at Warragul in a Maiden. Can feature with the right run. WILD LARRY (5) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
